tspan.tspan: Alpaca4d can be downloaded from: https://www.food4rhino.com/app/Alpaca4d
Follow the instructions to install Alpaca4d:
Create a new folder and rename it
Right-click on Alpaca4d.ghpy and Unblock the file.
Create a new folder and rename it
Alpaca4d plug-in will be found in the Alpaca4d tab of Grasshopper.
